<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-PT">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Análise do catálogo falhou — MarketPilot</title>
  <style>
    /* Inline styles for email client compatibility */
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      color: #0a1230;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 16px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e1e5ec;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px 36px;
    }
    .brand {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #00113a;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #00113a;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7896;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .reason-box {
      background: #f5f7fa;
      border: 1px solid #edf0f5;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .reason-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #3a4560;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .reason-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #0a1230;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #00113a;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .help-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7896;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid #edf0f5;
      padding-top: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #6b7896;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="brand">MarketPilot</div>

      <h1>A análise do catálogo não completou</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Olá<% if (it.customerName) { %> <%= it.customerName %><% } %>, encontrámos um problema durante a análise do teu catálogo Worten.
      </p>

      <div class="reason-box">
        <p class="reason-label">Motivo</p>
        <p class="reason-text"><%= it.failureReason %></p>
      </div>

      <p class="help-text">
        Para retomar o processo, valida novamente a tua chave de API Worten.
        O MarketPilot irá reiniciar a análise automaticamente após a validação.
      </p>

      <a href="<%= it.keyUrl %>" class="cta-btn">
        Tentar novamente →
      </a>

      <p class="help-text">
        Se o problema persistir, contacta-nos em
        <a href="mailto:suporte@marketpilot.pt" style="color: #00113a; font-weight: 600;">suporte@marketpilot.pt</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p style="margin: 0;">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MarketPilot · Repricing automatizado para o Worten</p>
      <p style="margin: 4px 0 0;">
        Este email foi enviado porque a tua conta MarketPilot requer atenção.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
